{"tid":2090350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子疑墮樓倒臥銅鑼灣行車道　再遭巴士捲入車底不治","createTime":"2020-07-02T06:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T01:50:18.000Z","uid":135488,"like":9,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd875eb4951b3a4a1b5bffeb4ba0a27603ce01d","tid":2090350,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"【橙訊】銅鑼灣一名年約30歲的男子清晨懷疑倒臥軒尼詩道路中，被一輛駛經的巴士捲入車底，消防救出送院後證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事發於清晨5時13分，一輛往維園方向行駛的N8P新巴，駛至軒尼詩道555號，百德新街附近時疑收掣不及，將事主捲入車底，困於左前輪前方。<br />\n<br />\n消防接報後花約20分鐘從車底救出傷者，昏迷送律敦治醫院搶救，於早上6時46分證實不治。警方列交通意外有人死亡調查，但不排除男子從附近大廈高處墮下，登上怡和街1號香港大廈作進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n巴士擋風玻璃及車頭沒有碰撞痕跡，據悉車長駛至現場前已見到事主倒卧路中，雖已減速但仍將他捲入車底。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2020/07/02/010153924.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2020%2F07%2F02%2F010153924.shtml&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8FznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=6ebe2a57\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2020/07/02/010153924.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"03121837f1707ea1d5fef631f9b34c461b888d52","tid":2090350,"uid":522,"like":70,"dislike":11,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fc02cb4b0bd5c2f1c728081d99a33da99a0e8d","tid":2090350,"uid":8014,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:23:31.000Z","msg":"国安咁早開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3968f3bd5c64f4576785b578f50a8c3bcb655ba6","tid":2090350,"uid":9116,"like":75,"dislike":3,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:24:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪，垃圾橙新聞都睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b499af14728d33c81b90c6c261611a17ec26f2f","tid":2090350,"uid":52283,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"昨日被捕手足？"},{"pid":"937fea20507227f4d5d012b7ca9ff7001a935c19","tid":2090